      <title>受股市推动，加州公务员退休基金 2024 财年收益增长 9.3%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/calpers-posts-9-3-gain-for-fiscal-2024-driven-by-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州公共雇员退休系统报告其最新财年增长了 9.3%，回报主要来自公共股权投资和私人债务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/calpers-posts-9-3-gain-for-fiscal-2024-driven-by-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 17:21:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
